<br>
In the past 3 years I can only name maybe 6 books I read basically non stop and didnt feel I had to wade my way through.<br>
<br>
Fallen Angels<br>
Animal Farm<br>
All Quiet on the Western Front<br>
Huck Finn<br>
Narrative of the Life of Frederick Douglass<br>
LoTR: Two Towers<br>
Harry Potter #4 (don't laugh, its a good book).<br>
<br>
